Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.24,0:02:07.71,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:121246,127711}Maya's Helen Keller impressed the audience\Nwith a different style from Ayumi's.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.71,0:02:14.46,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:127711,134468}In the meantime, her missing mother\Nwas spending her days in a hospital in Nagano…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.46,0:02:20.18,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:134468,140182}…and Maya was being nominated for\NBest Supporting Actress at the Academy Awards.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.18,0:02:27.18,Episode title,[title],0,0,0,,{TIME:141183,147189}{\an5\pos(766,700)\fscy95\blur1\fad(400,0)}—Episode 22—\NNew Doors
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.02,0:02:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:148023,149149}See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.56,0:02:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:150567,152319}Where are you going, Maya?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.65,0:02:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:152653,153862}Oh, Rei.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.86,0:02:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:153862,160202}I'm going back to Yokohama to see if the owners\Nof Manpuku Ken found out where my mother is.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.20,0:02:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:160202,163789}Maya, what are you talking about?\NToday is the awards day.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.78,0:02:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:163789,167709}She's supposed to call you\Nwhen she finds out where your mother is.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.70,0:02:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:167709,171588}Now, get ready,\Nor you'll be made ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.58,0:02:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:171588,173423}Hurry, hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.47,0:03:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:178470,180847}It's almost time to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.84,0:03:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:180847,181598}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.34,0:03:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:182349,185060}What should I do about the purple roses?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.43,0:03:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:186436,188689}Should I arrange\Nto send some to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.44,0:03:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:190440,195904}Tonight's party will be the first big award\Nfor Ms. Kitajima Maya.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.98,0:03:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:196988,199366}You must be misunderstanding something.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.36,0:03:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:199366,200784}Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.78,0:03:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:200784,205455}Why should I have to\Nsend her some purple roses?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.45,0:03:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:205455,207124}Because you love her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.12,0:03:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:207124,208208}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.20,0:03:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:208208,209710}Or is it because of guilt?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.50,0:03:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:217509,219469}You think I love her?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.46,0:03:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:219469,222347}No way. Don't be silly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.34,0:03:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:222347,227602}Mr. Masumi, you are denying\Nyour own emotions.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.60,0:03:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:227602,234067}You understand her talent better than anyone,\Nand you truly love her true self.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.06,0:03:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:234067,239489}But, whenever you interact with her,\Nyou act very cold because of your social status.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.48,0:04:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:239489,245829}To escape feeling guilty, you send her\Npurple roses and keep on encouraging her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.82,0:04:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:245829,249750}You are Mr. Purple Rose.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.66,0:04:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:250667,253420}But that's just cowardly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.71,0:04:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:254713,257591}Why don't you throw away\Nyour mask as Mr. Purple Rose…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.59,0:04:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:257591,262345}…and show affection as who you\Nreally are, Mr. Hayami Masumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.84,0:04:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:263847,265015}Mr. Masumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.68,0:04:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:268685,270520}You are acting strange today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.98,0:04:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:274983,276318}Please arrange the ride.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.31,0:04:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:277319,278195}Yes sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.07,0:04:46.87,Retrospective,,0,0,0,,{TIME:281072,286870}…and show affection as who\Nyou really are, Mr. Hayami Masumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.25,0:04:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:297255,298590}Here's your seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.59,0:05:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:298590,300050}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.72,0:05:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:309726,311853}This way, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.77,0:05:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:318777,320987}Metropolitan Entertainment\Nis doing great this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.65,0:05:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:322656,325367}Look at how beautiful she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.36,0:05:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:325367,328203}As soon as she steps in,\Nthe whole place becomes brighter.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.20,0:05:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:328203,330330}She was born to be a star.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.33,0:05:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:330330,331331}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.08,0:05:36.75,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:334084,336753}She's so confident.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.75,0:05:41.13,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:336753,341132}It must be some kind of mistake that I have more\Nof a chance at winning the award than she does.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.13,0:05:42.75,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:341132,342759}Yes, it's just a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.59,0:05:47.72,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:343592,347722}I always wake myself\Njust before the best part.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.76,0:05:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:349766,358358}Ladies and gentlemen,\Nlet us start the Academy Awards.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.94,0:06:03.53,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:358942,363530}The nominations for the awards and their\Npresentations were carried out by divisions…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.53,0:06:08.15,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:363530,368159}…such as Music Division, Traditional Dance\NDivision, and Western Music Division.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.41,0:06:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:368410,370704}Now, the Stage Drama Division.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.70,0:06:20.13,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:373707,380130}After many awards, the\NBest Supporting Actor was announced.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.13,0:06:23.50,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:380130,383508}Then it was time for the\NBest Supporting Actress award.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.05,0:06:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:386052,387804}The award for\NBest Supporting Actress…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.43,0:06:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:390432,393894}…goes to Helen Keller in\N"The Miracle Worker"…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.15,0:06:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:400150,401526}…Kitajima Maya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.41,0:06:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:410410,411828}Ms. Kitajima Maya, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.49,0:06:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:414497,416750}Please come to the stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.37,0:06:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:417375,419878}M-Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.92,0:07:05.59,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:423924,425592}This must be a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.59,0:07:06.67,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:425592,426676}A dream…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.80,0:07:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:426801,431598}The Academy Award for\NBest Supporting Actress: Kitajima Maya.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.59,0:07:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:431598,434809}Your performance in "The Miracle Worker"\Nhas a freshness…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.80,0:07:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:434809,440482}…that has never been seen before\Nand lends tremendous emotion to the play.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.48,0:07:23.23,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:440482,443234}I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.23,0:07:25.27,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:443234,445278}That's why.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.27,0:07:27.53,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:445278,447530}I see, I know now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.70,0:07:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:450700,454621}Oh, I feel like I'm still dreaming,\Nbut ouch…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.20,0:07:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:456205,457916}…it's not a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.54,0:07:44.96,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:460543,464965}Then the Best Actor and Best Actress\Nwere announced.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.96,0:07:50.59,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:464965,470595}Himekawa Utako won the Best Actress\Naward for her role as Annie Sullivan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.84,0:07:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:472847,476351}What an irony that her mother\Nand her rival both got awarded.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.35,0:08:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:476351,480522}But it will make the best headline.\N"The Defeat of a Genius Actress, Himekawa Ayumi."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.98,0:08:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:486987,487654}Ayumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.54,0:08:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:499541,501543}Congratulations, Mama.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.54,0:08:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:501543,503628}Thank you, Ayumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.96,0:08:28.04,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:505964,508049}"Mama", huh…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.04,0:08:29.13,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:508049,509134}Mother…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.05,0:08:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:510051,511720}Congratulations, Maya.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.47,0:08:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:513471,516266}Thank you, Ayumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.26,0:08:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:516266,519436}But I still don't think\Nyou defeated me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.81,0:08:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:519811,523189}I finally understood\Nwhen I heard the award.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.18,0:08:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:523189,526484}I still think I played\Nthe perfect Helen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.48,0:08:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:526484,533116}If you'd have played a perfect Helen better\Nthan I did, then I'd have really lost this award.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.28,0:08:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:535285,536286}But…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.28,0:08:59.53,Retrospective,,0,0,0,,{TIME:536286,539539}Your performance in "The Miracle Worker"…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.53,0:09:02.33,Retrospective,,0,0,0,,{TIME:539539,542333}…has brought a freshness\Nthat has never been seen before.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.33,0:09:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:542333,544294}Your Helen was a new Helen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.29,0:09:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:544294,547756}This means that your Helen and mine\Nwere totally different people.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.75,0:09:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:547756,551676}I have regained my confidence\Nthat mine was truly a perfect Helen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.34,0:09:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:552343,553053}Ayumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.93,0:09:20.47,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:555930,560477}After the awards were given,\Nthe reception was held.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.68,0:09:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:560685,565482}There is no contention in that Metropolitan\NEntertainment monopolized all twelve divisions.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.48,0:09:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:565482,570445}It is no wonder why your father can leave the\Nbusiness up to you with no worries, Mr. Masumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.73,0:09:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:570737,575366}I bet he would be even more\Nat ease if you got married now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.36,0:09:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:575366,578203}Are you seeing anyone right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.20,0:09:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:578203,580622}No, unfortunately, not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.62,0:09:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:580622,583666}Well, we hear\Nyou are a workaholic.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.59,0:09:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:591591,594052}Would you like to dance with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.51,0:09:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:595512,597764}Congratulations for your award.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.76,0:09:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:597764,599933}T-Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.93,0:10:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:599933,603061}An award-winning star\Nshould not be a wallflower.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.06,0:10:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:603061,604521}I don't know how to dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.56,0:10:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:608566,611236}That's okay.\NJust follow my lead.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.79,0:10:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:623790,625667}Good, you're doing fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.66,0:10:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:625667,628545}Why did you ask me to dance?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.54,0:10:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:628545,632674}You were the vanguard in promoting\NMetropolitan Entertainment.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.84,0:10:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:635844,637804}Everyone's watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.80,0:10:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:637804,640098}Just let them.\NIt will be good advertisement.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.09,0:10:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:640098,641307}Advertisement?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.30,0:10:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:641307,643518}You will be a star.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.51,0:10:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:643518,644394}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.39,0:10:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:644394,646604}You can't be a star if you are shy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.60,0:10:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:646604,648273}You have to learn how to sell yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.27,0:10:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:648273,651401}You can't be successful with just your talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.40,0:10:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:651401,655780}Why… Why are you\Ntelling me all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.78,0:11:01.11,Retrospective,,0,0,0,,{TIME:655780,661119}Why don't you, as Hayami Masumi,\Nshow your affection to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.49,0:11:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:661494,663079}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.07,0:11:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:663079,666624}I don't want to break\Na golden egg before it hatches.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.00,0:11:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:667000,670461}I won't be a golden egg\Nfor Metropolitan Entertainment!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.46,0:11:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:670461,671588}Never!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.63,0:11:22.89,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:681639,682891}This feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.31,0:11:35.32,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:693318,695320}That summer…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.40,0:11:41.32,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:698406,701326}…he's Mr. Purple Rose?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.86,0:11:42.95,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:701868,702952}No way!
Comment: 0,0:11:54.75,0:11:54.75,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:714756,714756}Eyecatch
Comment: 0,0:11:58.50,0:11:58.50,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:718509,718509}#Eyecatch
Comment: 0,0:12:01.47,0:12:01.47,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:721471,721471}Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.28,0:12:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:743284,745870}You are too young\Nfor the love scene, little girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.87,0:12:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:745870,748581}What happened? Has the heat\Nfrom the hall affected you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.96,0:12:35.96,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:753962,755964}No way.\NThat cold bastard can't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.96,0:12:37.79,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:755964,757799}It's just a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.79,0:12:41.34,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:757799,761344}Did she notice?\NNo, she couldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.47,0:12:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:767475,768977}Hello, Miss Tsukikage.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.97,0:12:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:768977,771187}Did you come to see\Nyour good student's award presentation?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.18,0:12:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:771187,775275}A good student?\NYes, some future good students.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.65,0:13:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:778653,780488}"Future good students"?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.24,0:13:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:784242,787078}Everyone, we have\Na surprise guest here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.07,0:13:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:787078,790456}A phenomenal actress,\Na lily of the stage drama world…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.45,0:13:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:790456,794252}…and the actress from "The Crimson Goddess",\NMiss Tsukikage Chigusa.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.25,0:13:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:794252,798298}The teacher of Himekawa Utako,\Nwho won Best Actress award…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.29,0:13:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:798298,803511}…and also of Kitajima Maya,\Nthe Best Supporting Actress.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.14,0:13:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:809142,812645}How are you, Miss Tsukikage?\NAny words of celebration?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.27,0:13:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:813271,817025}Yes. Both Helens have\Nsome extraordinary talents.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.02,0:13:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:817025,821738}I must say they are suited to be\Ncandidates for "The Crimson Goddess".
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.73,0:13:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:821738,825575}Ms. Kitajima Maya, Ms. Himekawa Ayumi.\NPlease come forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.45,0:13:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:829454,834917}Ayumi, would you like to practice\Nfor "The Crimson Goddess" with Maya here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.91,0:13:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:834917,837003}Miss Tsukikage…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.50,0:13:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:837503,838670}Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.67,0:14:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:838670,842800}I would love to.\NI would love to, Miss Tsukikage.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.34,0:14:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:844344,847055}Everyone, I would like\Nto take advantage of this opportunity…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.05,0:14:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:847055,850350}…to introduce the two candidates\Nfor "The Crimson Goddess":
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.35,0:14:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:850350,852769}Kitajima Maya and Himekawa Ayumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.93,0:14:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:853936,856439}The battle has just begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.43,0:14:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:856439,861444}I will see how they grow\Nas actresses, and eventually…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.44,0:14:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:861444,866699}…choose one of the two\Nfor "The Crimson Goddess".
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.20,0:14:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:870203,871579}Ayumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.99,0:14:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:872997,874040}Maya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.75,0:14:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:882757,885385}You had the first move.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.84,0:14:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:885843,889222}I was going to purchase\N"The Crimson Goddess"…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.22,0:14:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:889222,894227}…and give actresses nationwide\Nthe opportunity to compete.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.22,0:14:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:894227,897522}To promote the name\Nof Metropolitan Entertainment?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.52,0:15:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:897522,903528}Can I at least still hope for\Nthe play rights, Miss Tsukikage?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.52,0:15:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:903528,906989}I wouldn't give up the play rights\Neven if I were dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.98,0:15:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:906989,912745}No more little tricks of yours,\Nsince we have many witnesses now. Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.25,0:15:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:920252,923047}There's a phone call for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.67,0:15:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:924674,927051}Hello.\NThis is Maya speaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.05,0:15:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:927051,928678}Oh, Sakurakōji!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.67,0:15:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:928678,930638}Congratulations.\NI'm impressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.63,0:15:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:930638,934267}You're the first 16 year-old\Nto win an Academy Award.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.26,0:15:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:934267,936686}Thank you.\NYes, I'm happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.68,0:15:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:938688,939814}…America?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.81,0:15:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:939814,942608}I'm leaving tomorrow at twelve o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.60,0:15:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:942608,945027}I'm going to go\Nto acting school there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.02,0:15:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:945027,947530}I want to start learning\Nfrom scratch.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.57,0:15:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:950575,954287}I'll come back\Nwith ability and confidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.28,0:15:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:954287,956539}I'll be there,\Nat the airport tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.53,0:15:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:956539,959917}{\t(1878,3378,\1c&H101010&\3c&H101010&\4c&H101010&)}I'll be there, Sakurakōji.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.54,0:16:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:961544,962837}See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.38,0:16:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:964380,967049}Maya, your mother called.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.04,0:16:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:967049,968550}What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.55,0:16:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:968550,973639}The lady from Manpuku Ken\Njust called the landlord.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.63,0:16:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:973639,977268}She heard from your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.73,0:16:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:983733,988988}Hey, you keep looking at your watch.\NAre you expecting someone important?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.40,0:16:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:990406,992533}No, no one.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.53,0:16:37.49,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:992533,997497}Manpuku Ken
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.03,0:16:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:993034,995161}About eight o'clock\Nin the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.16,0:16:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:995161,997622}She said she was fine\Nand not to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.62,0:16:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:997622,1001042}I asked her where she was,\Nbut then she hung up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.04,0:16:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1001042,1002460}Is that so…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.46,0:16:44.46,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:1002460,1004462}Fukui Hospital
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.79,0:16:51.17,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1004795,1011177}Maya, I've lost my sight,\Nbut I can still see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.17,0:16:53.26,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1011177,1013262}I'm always watching you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.30,0:16:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1016307,1019352}Next time she calls, I'll be sure\Nto find out where she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.35,0:17:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1019352,1021771}So don't feel bad, Maya.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.77,0:17:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1021771,1023356}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.02,0:17:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1028027,1029362}Sakurakōji.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.82,0:17:15.28,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1032823,1035284}Maya, I'll do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.32,0:17:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1039329,1040831}A TV series?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.83,0:17:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1040831,1044502}He brought the offer\Nfrom the TV station for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.50,0:17:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1044502,1048798}He also has a television series for Ayumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.96,0:17:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1049966,1052843}Masumi must be caring for you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.84,0:17:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1052843,1055680}To be fair to the candidates\Nof "The Crimson Goddess".
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.64,0:17:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1057640,1064605}{\fs70}Masumi finally feels like letting the two candidates,\NMaya and Ayumi, grow for "The Crimson Goddess".
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.48,0:17:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1065481,1067567}A TV series for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.36,0:17:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1069360,1076659}Maya, I don't know how well your act will carry\Nto television, or how well you'll do in the TV world.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.65,0:17:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1076659,1077702}Teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.70,0:18:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1077702,1082999}You might become a star,\Nyou might not.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.99,0:18:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1082999,1086377}You might become worthless as an actress.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.87,0:18:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1086877,1087878}Teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.13,0:18:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1089130,1091966}Any route you take,\Nthe road will be rough and bumpy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.96,0:18:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1091966,1094051}I… I…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.88,0:18:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1094885,1096345}What can I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.34,0:18:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1096345,1099432}Should I decline?\NTeacher?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.43,0:18:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1099432,1102602}It is up to you\Nto make that decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.01,0:18:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1103019,1104477}Teacher…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.52,0:18:31.11,Retrospective,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1107523,1111110}You might even become worthless as an actress.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.98,0:18:35.07,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1111986,1115072}What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.07,0:18:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1117073,1119284}{\t(1211,2211,\1c&H101010&\3c&H101010&\4c&H101010&)}Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.66,0:18:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1122663,1124832}Okay, let her in.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.37,0:18:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1125374,1127001}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.29,0:18:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1130296,1132757}Hello, little girl.\NWelcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.75,0:18:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1132757,1134550}H-Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.55,0:18:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1134550,1136552}Don't be so nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.55,0:18:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1136552,1139930}I see. This is the first time\Nyou've been here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.93,0:19:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1139930,1141724}You can have a seat there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.72,0:19:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1141724,1145061}No, thank you. I'm just here\Nto answer your proposal.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.18,0:19:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1147188,1150608}I… I accept your offer\Nfor the TV series.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.60,0:19:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1150608,1157531}Good. I thought you'd reject it,\Nsince you don't like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.53,0:19:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1157531,1159492}What made you decide?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.11,0:19:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1161118,1164330}Do you want to be know on\Ntelevision and become a star?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.33,0:19:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1164330,1166123}This is for my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.12,0:19:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1166123,1168417}Your mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.41,0:19:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1168417,1172171}If I'm on TV, my mother\Nmight see me someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.17,0:19:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1172171,1174924}Then I might be able to find her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.92,0:19:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1174924,1176509}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.50,0:19:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1176509,1183432}{\fs72}Also, I'd like to thank you for this one, but I don't\Nintend to owe Metropolitan Entertainment a favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.43,0:19:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1183432,1185351}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.81,0:19:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1189814,1193067}She had the upper hand, Mr. Masumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.06,0:19:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1193067,1194568}Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.32,0:20:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1196320,1202785}Even if it's difficult, she has to keep on\Nwalking without looking back once she starts.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.53,0:20:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1203536,1206622}She finally started walking, all by herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.37,0:20:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1207373,1211502}Oh, that Mr. Purple Rose guy\Nyou mentioned before.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.50,0:20:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1211502,1214922}She doesn't need him anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.92,0:20:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1214922,1215506}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.11,0:20:47.66,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:1243117,1247663}Maya has moved forward to a new world,\Nfrom the stage to television.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.74,0:20:52.96,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:1248748,1252960}Ayumi, who has refused\Nall television offers in the past…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.96,0:20:56.71,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:1252960,1256714}…has accepted the new challenge\Nand jumped into the new world as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.92,0:20:58.88,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1256922,1258883}Maya, do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.88,0:21:06.47,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1258883,1266474}Try and see how much your acting ability\Non stage will work for television.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.47,0:21:09.68,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1267475,1269685}Go on ahead, Maya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.68,0:21:15.44,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1269685,1275441}Be destroyed as an actress,\Nor overcome it and jump even further ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.44,0:21:21.44,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1275441,1281447}What's important for you\Nis how you will grow as a person.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.69,0:21:25.03,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1282698,1285034}Ayumi, I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.03,0:21:29.07,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1285034,1289079}You'll not only notice my freshness\Nand originality, but also my ability…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.07,0:21:32.04,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1289079,1292041}…and someday…!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.17,0:21:45.22,Retrospective,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1302176,1305221}The battle has just began.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.01,0:21:50.51,Retrospective,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1306013,1310518}I will see how they grow as actresses…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.51,0:21:57.85,Retrospective,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1310518,1317858}…and eventually choose the one of the two\Nfor "The Crimson Goddess".
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.32,0:22:16.12,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1330329,1336126}The roads you take might be different,\Nbut your destination is the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.12,0:22:21.63,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1336126,1341632}Now, both of you,\Nstart walking towards your goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.30,0:22:27.63,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:1344301,1347638}Now, new doors have been opened.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.63,0:22:32.97,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:1347638,1352977}That was also the start\Nof a new maze of challenges.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.31,0:22:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1362319,1364113}Rolling, action!
